@startuml kv_client_triage_read_step
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontName "SansSerif"
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title KV Client 定位定界（步骤2: 读路径 Get/MGet）

actor "测试/开发/Agent" as T
participant "client1\nSDK" as C
participant "worker1\n入口Worker" as W1
participant "worker2\n元数据" as W2
participant "worker3\n数据副本" as W3
participant "OS/syscall" as OS
participant "URMA" as U

T -> C : 发起 Get/MGet
activate C

C -> C : PreGet 参数校验
alt 参数非法
  note right of C
    责任团队: 接口调用方/业务方
    现象: K_INVALID
    建议: 核对key数量/timeout/offset
  end note
  C --> T : 失败(K_INVALID)
  deactivate C
  return
end

C -> U : PrepareUrmaBuffer
alt UB准备失败
  note right of U
    责任团队: RDMA/URMA团队(性能归因)
    现象: fallback to TCP/IP payload
    建议: 功能可继续，性能退化优先查UB池
  end note
  C -> C : 降级TCP继续
end

C -> W1 : stub_->Get + RetryOnError
activate W1
alt 1001/1002/19 重试耗尽
  note right of W1
    责任团队: RPC/网络中间件团队(优先)
    建议: 无worker入口日志=>网络;
          有入口日志=>worker或下游慢
  end note
  W1 --> C : 返回RPC错误
  deactivate W1
  C --> T : 失败(RPC)
  deactivate C
  return
end

W1 -> W2 : QueryMeta
activate W2
alt etcd/master异常
  note right of W2
    责任团队: 元数据/控制面团队
    现象: etcd unavailable / Query from master failed
  end note
end
W2 --> W1 : 元数据结果
deactivate W2

W1 -> W3 : 远端拉取对象
activate W3
W3 -> U : urma_write/urma_read + poll/wait_jfc
alt URMA完成队列或读写失败
  note right of U
    责任团队: RDMA/URMA团队
    现象: 1004 / K_RUNTIME_ERROR / 1006
    建议: 查设备、CQ、连接稳定性
  end note
end
W3 --> W1 : 远端结果/last_rc
deactivate W3

W1 --> C : rpc get response
deactivate W1

C -> OS : mmap + payload组装
alt mmap失败或payload越界
  note right of OS
    责任团队: OS团队(映射) 或 数据面协议团队(越界)
    现象: Get mmap entry failed / UB payload overflow
    建议: 区分同机SHM问题还是返回payload不一致
  end note
  C --> T : 失败(5/6等)
  deactivate C
  return
end

C --> T : 成功/部分成功
deactivate C

@enduml
